metadata.name: CatBlox x TBT Bracket Challenge
metadata.description:
Welcome to the first-ever officially-licensed interactive NFT bracket challenge. In partnership with TBT (The Basketball Tournament on ESPN) featuring 64 teams, 6,400 dynamic free-mint NFTs with AR capability, many redeemable prizes and one true champion.

TBT airs only on the ESPN family of channels. Watch on cable, stream through your favorite provider, or stream internationally from Europe, Africa, and Middle East at espnplayer.com

Learn more about CatBlox Studios at catblox.xyz
